Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.11,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shady Detective Trap{\i0}....
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I thought they would \Nhave a tough time in Jack,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.87,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but their ranking has settled \Ndown nicely on the surveys.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.99,0:00:21.83,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It looks like we all work well together.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, snap out of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.67,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.34,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And now?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm coming now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.43,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.89,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It looks like...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.40,0:00:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro collapsed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been one thing after another for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The volume cover and the \Nfront page color spread...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro's been having to deal with more and more responsibilities,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we're together, we get too absorbed and I didn't realize his condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.42,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For a high school student, \Nit's probably the worst thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in agonizing over it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.01,0:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he regained consciousness and was brought to the hospital,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he should be okay for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important right now is checking up on his condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything else comes after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know yet; \Nthey're still examining him.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I meant you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's like you said...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to do this \Nwhile still in school, after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of my son.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mashiro Moritaka's mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I apologize!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.52,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we possibly apologize for letting things get to this point?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know \Nwhat his condition's like.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is something \Nmy son chose for himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the boy's guardian?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Saiko—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is Mashiro okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, he and Mashiro \Nare a pair of mangakas,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're from the publisher.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us know his \Ncondition as well, if you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.93,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Katou, you can go back now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.81,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.77,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, you need to \Nremove a portion of his liver?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting it simply, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the manuscript here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to draw here in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.29,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The front page color spread is the greatest chance we've been given.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw it here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it here!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, he's supposed to rest, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's tending towards malnutrition.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.57,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll also need to be hospitalized for three months after the surgery...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months...?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't die so easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't die now,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but your condition will worsen if you keep pushing yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't an illness you \Ncan recover from naturally.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to stay hospitalized \Nand undergo treatment...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me draw here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being serialized \Nin a weekly magazine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, you need to rest—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't rest on a weekly publication!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go on hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when we've finally gotten popular...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't rest now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, we appreciate \Nyour determination.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But shouldn't curing \Nyour illness come first?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all people should understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different from a long-running manga taking a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.50,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you had only two more pages of chapter 19 to pen-in?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we'll leave 19 to \Nthe assistants to finish up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll reconsider what \Nhappens after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to pen-in the characters myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it take you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Three to four hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.28,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to take a day to do the color spread that goes with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Doctor?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.07,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My son isn't a manga-drawing robot!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to persuade him, but I got caught up in it...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,While he's in the hospital,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take responsibility \Nand make sure he rests.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to consult the higher-ups before deciding what to do next.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, talk to you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro will have to be hospitalized for a while, it seems.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll tell us more tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hiatus, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there's no point \Nin us getting depressed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What we should be doing now
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.12,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is finishing up the 16 pages of chapter 19 that are penned-in.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this the \Nbest manuscript so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.84,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.33,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.81,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Why is Saiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin, it's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you to be making calls?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked them to let me go to the bathroom by myself, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, bring the \Nmanuscript to the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely won't let it fall behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pros, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.83,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My hospital room is empty \Naside from one old guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can do it without \Nthe doctor noticing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much easier than \NNakai doing it in the park!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait until you've fully recovered.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.10,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to drop \Nthe ball on this now!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stall for three months, we'll lose the readers we finally pulled in!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll undergo the surgery.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only day I won't be able to draw!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a color spread!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our chance to surpass Eiji!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about repaying Hattori?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The future of {\i1}Trap{\i0} starts here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.28,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Visiting hours start at 3 PM.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At 3, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro said he wants to do the penning-in of the characters himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But that'll be tough, \Nrealistically speaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And not only that;
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to rethink serializing \Na high school student.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Publish the finished 16 pages.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the other two pages,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll publish one of them with the announcement of the hiatus that begins next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And listening to your story,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems that Mashiro can't even touch a pen in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep visiting the hospital and monitor the situation as much as you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be obvious, but the health of the author comes first.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the doctor's orders, \Nnot the will of the author.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely a safe surgery, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you absolutely, \Npositively, 100% certain?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's a simple surgery, so there shouldn't be any problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery is two weeks from the 10th.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be hospitalized for \Nat least three months.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll probably be on \Nhiatus during that time...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.91,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko asked me to bring the \Nmanuscript to the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I would.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I considered his feelings, I couldn't answer any other way.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's really your friend, \Nyou need to stop him!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? That's pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I don't want\N to go on hiatus either!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rankings went up, \Nwe got a color spread...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in Saiko's place, \NI'd draw even if it meant dying!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't draw manga if you're dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you don't die,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a bad idea to draw \Nmanga while in bad health...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.83,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,440)}I want to have a long-running popular manga ranked first place!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.63,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No matter how many years it takes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm and listen.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that an assistant should take care of the author.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.15,0:11:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need to do that,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and my mom should be here soon...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I already met your mom yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's not what I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.16,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin, where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.17,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to \Nbring the manuscript at 3!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, it's me, Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.09,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki? Why is she here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.96,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.88,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, I'll leave the {\i1}work{\i0} to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.47,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You don't need to emphasize "work" so much...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh, she looks like a doll!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.94,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I could never compete.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.56,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,She bowed before I did!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.32,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,She's really composed!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's okay for me to come in...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only supposed to meet after our dreams come true...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.75,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were going to meet me at my house a while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,an emergency...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.50,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm moving quickly towards realizing my dream...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I continue the serialization nonstop for a bit longer,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, even though it's a bit \Nembarrassing, I'll speak from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can at least talk, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.90,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to wait until {\i1}after{\i0} you recover to draw, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.71,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I won't let the manuscript fall behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.17,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin, hurry up and bring it here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.05,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Could he have...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't promise
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that you won't draw until you're \Nreleased from the hospital...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hate you for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll hate me for something like that,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then go ahead and hate me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave until you \Nsay you won't draw!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll really hate you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.49,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, knowing \Nthat I can't hate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you can't, \Nyou're worse for saying you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.67,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I've liked you for eight years, there's no way I could hate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.43,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's the first time she's said she likes me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight years?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since 4th grade.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buy me candied apples!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to get\N more cavities, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Candied apples!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I really like this painting.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well done.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny how it's spelled "Saiko" but read like "Moritaka."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.68,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Candied apples!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, your art's on display again?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, so whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to be a \Nmangaka when you grow up?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your art too different?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics are what's important, stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go to the \Ncardboard boat tournament.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1130)}Ever since I saw that painting...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, \NI was really interested in you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I lived close to the school,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd look for you on the way to and from it...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in 5th grade...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the compass my uncle uses!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You put ink on it and draw!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for pro mangakas!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just buying a \Ncompass for math, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's 4,500 yen...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I really, really want it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama, how much do you have on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.01,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have 500 yen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Saiko, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, how much do you have?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,About 150 yen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.15,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked how your eyes sparkled when you looked at the compass.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.36,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At the swim meet, I was watching you constantly, trying to convey my feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.87,0:15:37.79,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,That's when I first noticed her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.79,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the same middle school and both got placed in Class 3...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,500)}So after our dreams come true, please marry me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy I could die.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we die, our dreams won't come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.18,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always liked you, and you're irreplaceable to me now...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to stop drawing until you're released, for my sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,value manga more than me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't be compared.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both important,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you put it that way,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then manga is more important.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}M-Mashiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You came out...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw the manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga is great!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I feel just like Joe from {\i1}Ashita no Joe{\i0} when he went to his final match.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.66,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So Azuki couldn't stop him?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really pumped up right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and bring the manuscript!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.70,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there in 20...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, 15 minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for telling Azuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi's going on hiatus?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right now the editorial \Ndepartment is topsy turvy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.10,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of a good story that won't lose to {\i1}Trap{\i0}'s front page color spread.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to compete with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well he's sick, so nothing\N can be done about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to visit him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Which hospital is he in?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was Yakusa Municipal Hospital...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakusa Municipal, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.26,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we've seen each \Nother, you can come inside...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.57,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He has a girlfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.78,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And such a cute girl too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.53,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I guess manga wasn't \Nhis girlfriend, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost ran into your mom at the entrance!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the G pens.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some Crow quill \Npens and spoon pens too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot the ink!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have color pens, so I'll start with chapter 20's color page.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish chapter 19 by tomorrow,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you take it to the office right away, we should make it in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.03,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.03,0:18:51.36,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,She's gotten more mature,\N or prettier, you could say.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring the manuscript?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.07,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who \Nasked me to stop him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a guy, I guess?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.45,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you feel something when looking at him working so hard, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.60,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.30,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)}this is the first time I've seen him while he's drawing manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's HOSPITAL! {I took off some all caps before, but that was something like "YES!". This is just Niizuma being Niizuma so I think it's fine}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, this is a hospital! \NKeep your voice down!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the receipt please.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-sensei, I'm here!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working on your\N color page, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, you're not allowed\N to run inside a hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuujirou, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't good to interrupt someone's work.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad I came!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to run!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That cute girl is Mashiro's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have thought she was Takagi's...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.73,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks just like {\i1}Trap{\i0}'s heroine, Ami.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.19,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wouldn't think \Nyou were a Jack editor.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's cuter than Ami.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, what the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm arranging a substitute \Nmanuscript for {\i1}Trap{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro is drawing the \Nmanuscript in the hospital!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be awkward with \Njust the two of us here...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just too embarrassed \Nand can't look at your face.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.02,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, can you stay until I leave?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.07,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, hide the manuscript!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we should show it to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him know we're still \Ngonna make the deadline.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.75,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 20's color page is going well.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish penning-in chapter 19 tomorrow,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and it can be finalized soon after.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can draw in the hospital just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely won't let the \Nmanuscript fall behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.52,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.52,0:21:40.73,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No, stopping him is my job.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the nurse!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me draw—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Takagi, hurry up and call the nurse!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro is saying he's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, when you brought \Nthe manuscript here,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you were prepared to have him draw no matter what, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.59,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make him stop here, you shouldn't have brought it at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.68,0:22:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.56,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can draw without resting.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.71,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make our dreams come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.91,0:22:34.83,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I-I can't tell him to stop drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.97,0:24:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro collapsed?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.56,0:24:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Serializing while in high \Nschool was too tough, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.60,0:24:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My health is also kinda—
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.85,0:24:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.23,0:24:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.48,0:24:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Life-or-Death and Standstill.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I value my health more than my dreams.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.69,0:24:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida-shi!
