Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:21.90,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:28.41,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:35.04,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:41.38,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:50.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:56.35,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I fuel my passion until I succeed
