Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:09.36,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:15.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rise back up again and again and again
