Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:55.35,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In this world, every day is dull and full of nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:23:01.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cover my ears, trying to mute the noise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.53,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do people hurt each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.83,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the contradictory, overlapping shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:23.54,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the recesses of my heart, fallen into despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:26.42,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While carrying this pain in my chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.42,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,can I really dream of tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:36.43,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remembering the rainbow I found after the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:43.06,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I close my eyes; come fly with me into my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:46.52,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I have you, who shines so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:51.82,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can envision an everlasting rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:59.79,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And even remember the moonlight of night we met
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:06.75,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can picture them... countless times
